            "question": "How far in advance should we reach out?",
            "answer": "<p>Portrait sessions usually book 4-8 weeks out, while weddings and commercial projects often book several months in advance. If your date is close, it is still worth asking.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq-2": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Do you travel for weddings or brand shoots?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes. Framelight takes on destination weddings and brand work selectively throughout the year. Travel costs are quoted transparently based on scope and location.</p>"
          }
        },
